metadata.name: Regiment
metadata.description:
Blocks of Lisbon - Square format, detailed architectural images from the Portuguese city.

Regiment - The first in the Blocks of Lisbon collection. 
Formational parts of a building caught the strong Lisbon sun creating beautiful patterns in the architecture. 
Lisbon 2017  
Exposure: 1/800 second at f/8  
ISO: 64  
Focal Length: 35mm  
Camera: Nikon D810  
Lens: Zeiss
